<br>
World-all available space is build like a city. Over populated, heavily polluted. <br>
<br>
World- in a state of cold war, no trade or corresponding with other countries.<br>
<br>
World-mock peace government. Controlled by various powerful families (mobs)<br>
<br>
World- like current. Half or more population robots. All blue collar jobs taken over by machines.<br>
<br>
World- post-apocalyptic. In a state of environmental chaos. Lack of water and vegetation.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Hero- cookie cutter hero type. Strong, reliable, brave.<br>
<br>
Hero- cocky punk. Doesn’t really care about any except himself.<br>
<br>
Hero-whiney, annoying, weak, but determined.<br>
<br>
Hero- laid back, intelligent. A bit of a rouge. Somewhat arrogant<br>
<br>
Hero- Quite, calm. Slightly depressed. Barely talks.<br>
<br>
<br>
Supporting character- sly, cunning, thief<br>
<br>
Supporting character- loud, annoying, sarcastic<br>
<br>
Supporting character- indecisive. Confused.<br>
<br>
Supporting character- all muscle, no brain<br>
<br>
Supporting character- moral support. Cute and cheerful<br>
<br>
Supporting character- bossy, mean<br>
<br>
Supporting character- constant showoff. Gets themselves into trouble.<br>
<br>
Supporting character- a bit moody and sensitive, very wise<br>
<br>
Supporting character- dark, possibly a traitor or previous affiliation with villain<br>
<br>
Supporting character- calm, cool, barely shaken by anything<br>
<br>
<br>
Villain- government. One main evil guy.<br>
<br>
Villain- sorcerer/magical being <br>
<br>
Villain- insane scientist<br>
<br>
Villain- dark, shadowy, unknown<br>
<br>
Villian- tyrant/conquerer <br>
 <br>
These are just some basic ideas, anything can be added. What do you think? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ujefm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jefm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(10/7/01 1:04:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=342.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Team of fantasy/action writers</span><hr size=1> The world doesn't sound post apocalyptic...<br>
